"text_ar":"تَفَرَّغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~Y mina Al$~ugoli","text_ar":"تخلّى مِنَ الشُّغْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frg","text_ar":"فرغ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~Y liloEibaAdapi","text_ar":"تخلّى لِلْعِبَادَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made himself, vacant for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he confined himself exclusively to, the service of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also 1, in the latter part of the paragraph. In like manner, one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA^amori","text_ar":"لِلْاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaA","text_ar":"خَلَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made himself, vacant for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he confined himself exclusively to, the affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxal~awoA bixaliy~apK","text_ar":"تَخَلَّوْا بِخَلِيَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They confined themselves exclusively to a she-camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to she-camels, such as they termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xlyp","text_ar":"خلية"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHolubuwnahaA","text_ar":"يَحْلُبُونَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milking"},{"kind":"text","text":"only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~Y xaliy~apF","text_ar":"تخلّى خَلِيَّةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took for himself a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xly~p","text_ar":"خليّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~Y mina AlA^amori","text_ar":"تخلّى مِنَ الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu","text_ar":"عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 2. ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxal~ati AlA_ibilu bilaA raAEK","text_ar":"تَخَلَّتِ الاـِبِلُ بِلَا رَاعٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels were left to themselves without a pastor"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swE","text_ar":"سوع"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}